{"tid":2412074,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"醉男女的士內嘔吐失禁疑拒付清潔費 司機吹雞打人被捕","createTime":"2021-02-17T21:08:51.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-18T08:07:23.000Z","uid":29627,"like":30,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"2e7c0affbbfcd60b2e388285f76acd129e51c6aa","tid":2412074,"uid":29627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T21:08:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20210218/ONHXPDMZXFGDLBMDJ4M3CWWTBQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20210218%2FONHXPDMZXFGDLBMDJ4M3CWWTBQ%2F&d=3nH4Hj8OzEJ%2Fsn4LiTBSOnwvfzOYOHHotQSumXQzHeA%3D&h=9d95e337\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20210218%2FONHXPDMZXFGDLBMDJ4M3CWWTBQ%2F&h=a0358a1f\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20210218/ONHXPDMZXFGDLBMDJ4M3CWWTBQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n凌晨零時許，一對醉酒男女由元朗乘的士前往美孚蘭秀道。其間有人不勝酒力，於車內嘔吐，並懷疑失禁，的士駛至美孚新邨第六期一間便利店外停下，司機要求繳付清潔費，雙方疑因金額問題未能達成共識發生口角，其間司機召來一名行家到場，並一同用電筒襲擊兩名乘客。兩及乘客受輕傷報案，由接報救護員包紮送院。警員調查拘捕兩名涉案的士司機。案件列作襲擊致造成身體傷害。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/kiAi4WHJFnKwGC1n8EgshAsf_mA=/802x534/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/753PHU3CTZC73K4KB76UBVQPGM.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FkiAi4WHJFnKwGC1n8EgshAsf_mA%3D%2F802x534%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F753PHU3CTZC73K4KB76UBVQPGM.JPG&h=6f5f64c5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n嘔吐乘客疑失禁。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/QBVSV629xfL1CKngj53r5J31d4Q=/802x534/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/YTU6V77WZBHLBGYTTPXXIJHD4I.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FQBVSV629xfL1CKngj53r5J31d4Q%3D%2F802x534%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.i